{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1778467111647,"sessionID":"ses_1eb198eb3ffe3LeeBAZNTClA3K","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"functions.read:0","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/runner/work/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/__issue_context__.json"},"output":"<path>/home/runner/work/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/__issue_context__.json</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: {\n2:   \"body\": \"Please provide as much information as you can: \\n\\n* **Suggested term label:Ferritin-specific autophagy**\\n\\n\\n* **Definition (A ferritin-specific autophagic pathway leading to the release of the iron stored inside ferritin.)**\\n\\n\\n* **Reference, in format PMID:38714719, 25327288, 26436293**\\n(REQUIRED)\\n\\n* **Gene product name and ID to be annotated to this term: FTH1, NCOA4**\\n\\n\\n* **Parent term(s): GO:0006914 - Autophagy**\\n\\n\\n* **Children terms (if applicable)** Should any existing terms that should be moved underneath this new proposed term?\\n\\n\\n* **Synonyms (ferritinophagy - exact)**\\n\\n* **Cross-references**\\n* For enzymes, please provide RHEA and/or EC numbers. \\n* Can also provide MetaCyc, KEGG, Wikipedia, and other links.\\n\\n* **Any other information**\\n\",\n3:   \"comments\": [\n4:     {\n5:       \"id\": \"IC_kwDOAkAHws7grbwP\",\n6:       \"author\": {\n7:         \"login\": \"ValWood\"\n8:       },\n9:       \"authorAssociation\": \"MEMBER\",\n10:       \"body\": \"Adding with parent \\\"macroautophagy\\\"\\nand as ferritinophagy\\nexact synonym ferritin-specific autophagy\\n\\nstandardized def\\nThe selective degradation of ferritin to release iron by macroautophagy. \\n\\n\",\n11:       \"createdAt\": \"2026-01-19T17:29:56Z\",\n12:       \"includesCreatedEdit\": false,\n13:       \"isMinimized\": false,\n14:       \"minimizedReason\": \"\",\n15:       \"reactionGroups\": [],\n16:       \"url\": \"https://github.com/geneontology/go-ontology/issues/30894#issuecomment-3769482255\",\n17:       \