{"type":"text","timestamp":1778467454535,"sessionID":"ses_1eb198eb3ffe3LeeBAZNTClA3K","part":{"id":"prt_e14eba992001TGDFwZHziTGGzX","messageID":"msg_e14eba0db001Xa8WsaQsqV5pOQ","sessionID":"ses_1eb198eb3ffe3LeeBAZNTClA3K","type":"text","text":"All done.\n\n### What I did\n\n1. **Analyzed the issue** — clear request for a new selective autophagy term for ferritin degradation (ferritinophagy), with parent macroautophagy, synonym, and three PMIDs.\n\n2. **Researched & validated** — cached and confirmed the three PMIDs:\n   - **PMID:38714719** — *Structural basis for the intracellular regulation of ferritin degradation.*\n   - **PMID:25327288** — *Selective VPS34 inhibitor blocks autophagy and uncovers a role for NCOA4 in ferritin degradation and iron homeostasis in vivo.*\n   - **PMID:26436293** — *Ferritinophagy via NCOA4 is required for erythropoiesis and is regulated by iron dependent HERC2-mediated proteolysis.*\n\n3. **Consulted existing pattern** — examined sibling selective-autophagy terms (ribophagy, aggrephagy, lipophagy, proteaphagy, lysophagy, xenophagy) and followed the same structure: simple `is_a` to `macroautophagy`, no unnecessary logical over-specification.\n\n4. **Created the term** (`GO:7770069`) in `terms/GO_7770069.obo`, checked it in with `obo-checkin.pl`, and committed the change to `src/ontology/go-edit.obo`.\n\n5. **Validated** — OBO syntax (`robot convert`) and logical consistency (`robot reason -r ELK`) both passed.\n\n### New term\n\n| Field | Value |\n|-------|-------|\n| **ID** | GO:7770069 |\n| **Name** | ferritinophagy |\n| **Namespace** | biological_process |\n| **Definition** | The selective degradation of ferritin to release iron by macroautophagy. |\n| **Refs** | PMID:38714719, PMID:25327288, PMID:26436293 |\n| **Synonym** | ferritin-specific autophagy (EXACT) |\n| **Parent** | is_a GO:0016236 ! macroautophagy |\n| **Term tracker** | https://github.com/geneontology/go-ontology/issues/30894 |\n\n### Outputs created\n\n- `ISSUE_COMMENTS.md` — ready to post back on issue #30894\n- `PR_COMMENTS.md` — detailed PR description with rationale and checklist\n- Commit `f9053c6` on branch with `src/ontology/go-edit.obo` updated","time":{"start":1778467449234,"end":1778467454533}}}
